trans-unit.source: Contains the settings for the supported versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: 包含 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定支援版本的設定。

trans-unit.source: There are currently two versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol supported by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] 目前支援兩種版本的 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定：WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 和 WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005。

trans-unit.source: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 是由 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> 傳回，而 WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 則是由 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>傳回。

trans-unit.source: Returns the default version of WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定的預設版本。

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the default version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: 自 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> 衍生的執行個體，代表 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定的預設版本。

trans-unit.source: Gets version 1.1 of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: 取得 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定的 1.1 版。

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 version.
trans-unit.target: 自 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> 衍生的執行個體，代表 WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 版。

trans-unit.source: Gets the February 2005 version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: 取得 WS-ReliableMessaging 通訊協定的 2005 年 2 月版本。

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 version.
trans-unit.target: 自 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> 衍生的執行個體，代表 WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 版。
